msgstr "ኮዶቼን አስቀምጫለሁ"

#: jsapp/js/components/bigModal/mfaModals.tsx:350
msgid ""
"Enter this key into your authenticator app to generate a ##number##-digit "
"token"
msgstr "አሃዛዊ ተለዋጭ ለማመንጨት ይህንን ቁልፍ ወደ አረጋጋጭ ##number##መተግበሪያዎ ያስገቡ"

